rbeads.htm">"Anglican Prayer Beads"</a>. <i>King of Peace Episcopal Church</i>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20190201164947/http://www.kingofpeace.org/prayerbeads.htm">Archived</a> from the original on 1 February 2019.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=King+of+Peace+Episcopal+Church&amp;rft.atitle=Anglican+Prayer+Beads&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kingofpeace.org%2Fprayerbeads.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJesus+Prayer" class="Z3988"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id="cite_note-Mathewes-Green2009-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Mathewes-Green2009_10-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Mathewes-Green2009_10-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFFrederica_Mathewes-Green2009" class="citation book cs1">Frederica Mathewes-Green (2009). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=hHIG2hFP8QYC&amp;pg=PA76"><i>The Jesus Prayer: The Ancient Desert Prayer that Tunes the Heart to God</i></a>. Paraclete Press. p.\xa076–. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>\xa0<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-55725-659-1" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-55725-659-1"><bdi>978-1-55725-659-1</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Jesus+Prayer%3A+The+Ancient+Desert+Prayer+that+Tunes+the+Heart+to+God&amp;rft.pages=76-&amp;rft.pub=Paraclete+Press&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-55725-659-1&amp;rft.au=Frederica+Mathewes-Green&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DhHIG2hFP8QYC%26pg%3DPA76&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJesus+Prayer" class="Z3988"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="