cere în spiritualitatea ortodoxă</i> (<i>Prayer and silence in the Orthodox spirituality</i>), translation from <a href="/wiki/English_language" title="English language">English</a>, Christiana Ed., <a href="/wiki/Bucharest" title="Bucharest">Bucharest</a>, 2003, pp. 23, 26, <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>\xa0<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/973-8125-42-1" title="Special:BookSources/973-8125-42-1">973-8125-42-1</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id="cite_note-38"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-38">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="languageicon">(in Romanian)</span> Fr. Ioan de la Rarău, <i>Rugăciunea lui Iisus. Întrebări şi răspunsuri</i> (<i>Jesus Prayer. Questions and answers</i>), Panaghia Ed., Rarău Monastery, <a href="/wiki/Vatra_Dornei" title="Vatra Dornei">Vatra Dornei</a>, p. 97. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>\xa0<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-973-88218-6-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-973-88218-6-6">978-973-88218-6-6</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id="cite_note-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-39">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.dailygreece.com/2008/03/post_246.php">"greek news: Οι τρόποι της ευχής"</a>. Dailygreece.com. 1999-02-22<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2010-07-03</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=greek+news%3A+%CE%9F%CE%B9+%CF%84%CF%81%CF%8C%CF%80%CE%BF%CE%B9+%CF%84%CE%B7%CF%82+%CE%B5%CF%85%CF%87%CE%AE%CF%82&amp;rft.pub=Dailygreece.com&amp;rft.date=1999-02-22&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailygreece.com%2F2008%2F03%2Fpost_246.php&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJesus+Prayer" class="Z3988"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id