nei" title="Vatra Dornei">Vatra Dornei</a>, pp. 6, 12–15, 130, <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>\xa0<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-973-88218-6-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-973-88218-6-6">978-973-88218-6-6</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id="cite_note-kallistos-ware-37"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-kallistos-ware_37-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-kallistos-ware_37-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-kallistos-ware_37-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="languageicon">(in Romanian)</span> <i>Puterea Numelui sau despre Rugăciunea lui Iisus</i> (<i>The Power of the Name. The Jesus Prayer in Orthodox Spirituality</i>) in <a href="/wiki/Kallistos_Ware" title="Kallistos Ware">Kallistos Ware</a>, <i>Rugăciune şi tăcere în spiritualitatea ortodoxă</i> (<i>Prayer and silence in the Orthodox spirituality</i>), translation from <a href="/wiki/English_language" title="English language">English</a>, Christiana Ed., <a href="/wiki/Bucharest" title="Bucharest">Bucharest</a>, 2003, pp. 23, 26, <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>\xa0<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/973-8125-42-1" title="Special:BookSources/973-8125-42-1">973-8125-42-1</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id="cite_note-38"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-38">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="languageicon">(in Romanian)</span> Fr. Ioan de la Rarău, <i>Rugăciunea lui Iisus. Întrebări şi răspunsuri</i> (<i>Jesus Prayer. Questions and answers</i>), Panaghia Ed., Rarău Monastery, <a href="/wiki/Vatra_Dornei" title="Vatra Dornei">Vatra Dornei</a>, p. 97. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>\xa0<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-973-88218-6-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-973-88218-6-6">978-973-88218-6-6</a>.</span>\