ican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/speeches/2000/apr-jun/documents/hf_jp-ii_spe_20000525_jubilee-science_en.html">"For the Jubilee of Scientists"</a>. <i>Vatican.va</i>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180829000216/https://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/speeches/2000/apr-jun/documents/hf_jp-ii_spe_20000525_jubilee-science_en.html">Archived</a> from the original on 29 August 2018<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">16 March</span> 2019</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Vatican.va&amp;rft.atitle=For+the+Jubilee+of+Scientists&amp;rft.date=2000-05-25&amp;rft.au=Pope+John+Paul+II&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vatican.va%2Fholy_father%2Fjohn_paul_ii%2Fspeeches%2F2000%2Fapr-jun%2Fdocuments%2Fhf_jp-ii_spe_20000525_jubilee-science_en.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJesus+Prayer" class="Z3988"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id="cite_note-15"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFPope_John_Paul_II1996" class="citation web cs1"><a href="/wiki/Pope_John_Paul_II" title="Pope John Paul II">Pope John Paul II</a> (11 August 1996). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20070926231104/http://www.catholicculture.org/library/view.cfm?recnum=5660">"Eastern Theology Has Enriched the Whole Church"</a>. <i>CatholicCulture.org</i>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.catholicculture.org/library/view.cfm?recnum=5660">the original</a> on 26 September 2007<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">16 March</span> 2019</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=CatholicCulture.org&amp;rft.atitle=Eastern+Theology+Has+Enriched+the+Who